{q:"What is 'Sehri' during Ramadan?",o:["Evening prayer","The meal before dawn to start the fast","Breaking the fast","A festival"],a:"The meal before dawn to start the fast",e:"Muslims eat Suhoor before Fajr prayer."},
{q:"What is the significance of the 'Odwira' festival?",o:["Harvest and purification","Easter","Ramadan","Independence"],a:"Harvest and purification",e:"Odwira cleanses the stool and the state in Akan tradition."},
{q:"Which of the following promotes religious tolerance in Ghana?",o:["Interfaith marriage","Religious insults","Forcing conversion","Burning churches"],a:"Interfaith marriage",e:"Interfaith dialogue and marriage foster tolerance and unity."}
